File: Gupta associate, Iqbal Sharma. (eNCA) JOHANNESBURG - Gupta associate, Iqbal Sharma has been granted bail of R500,000. Sharma was previously denied bail after the court deemed him as a flight risk. WATCH:  Iqbal Sharma denied bail Sharma and three senior Free State government officials are facing fraud and money laundering charges. A R25-million tender was irregularly awarded to a company owned and controlled by Sharma. More details to follow